Body.Content:
We are announcing the availability of contract processing (preview), a new prebuilt AI Builder model.

How does this affect me?
The contract processing prebuilt model is designed to analyze and extract key fields and line items from contract entities. Templates are available to help you begin using this feature immediately in a cloud flow or canvas app.

What action do I need to take?
This message is for awareness and no action is required.

If you would like more information on this feature, please visit the Contract processing prebuilt model (preview) article.

Title: AI Builder - Introducing the new contract processing prebuilt model (preview)
